---
title: Quick Spiced Beef & Carrot Couscous Salad with Crumbly Cheese & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: How satisfying are juicy beef strips on a bed of fluffy carrot couscous? You'll have to make this delectable fusion dish to find out!
We've added a cooling creamy pesto dressing and a smattering of crumbly cheese to top it off. Simply delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-beef-carrot-couscous-salad-5bf42bad.jpg
